    dc:description "Figure 9. Macrocharacter of Cordyceps militaris a-e stromata and host of Cordyceps militaris (a collected from Daxing'an Mountains, Heilongjiang Province b collected from Ji'an County, Tonghua City, Jilin Province c, e collected from Changchun City, Jilin Province d collected from Qujin City, Huize County, Yunnan Province). Scale bars: 1 cm (a-e)." ;
